stories.title: Martyn pulverises ineffectual Bangladesh
stories.summary:
Damien Martyn: back with a bang    
 
 
 
A blistering assault by Damien Martyn pulverised Bangladesh as Australia took a 2-0 lead in the three-match one-day series with a ridiculously easy nine-wicket win at Cairns
